<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi>— <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kulottuṅkacoḻa<unclear>tevaṟku yāṇ</unclear>ṭu <num value="45">4 <g type="numeral">10</g> 5</num>- <unclear>Āvatu</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>kaṅkaikoṇṭacoḻavaḷaṉāṭṭup paṉaiyūrnāṭṭut tevatāṉan tiruvāmāttūr Apimāṉapū<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi>ṇatte
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rin=ta kaiykkoḷarkku taṇṭaṉāyakam Arayan pūmāṅkaḻalāṉa kulottuṅkacoḻap pallavaraiyan
<lb n="4"/>Āḷuṭaiyār Aḻakiyatevarkku vaitta tirunan=tā viḷakku 1 Ittirunan=tā viḷak<unclear>ku</unclear> Oṟukkum veṇṭuñ cāvā
<lb n="5"/>muvāp perāṭu toṇṇūṟṟāṟuṅ koṇṭu viṭa Ikkoyilil tiruvuṇṇāḻikai- <hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi> yārvacam Iṭṭa kācu
<lb n="6"/><num value="11"><g type="numeral">10</g> 1</num> Ikkācu patiṉonṟuṅ koṇṭu Āṭukoṇṭu Ittirunan=tā viḷakku Onṟuñ can=ti rātittavaṟ Erikkakaṭavo
<lb n="7" break="no"/>māṉom tiruvuṇṇāḻikai<hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi> yom <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="danda">.</g></supplied> Itu pa<hi rend="grantha">nmā heśva</hi> rar <hi rend="grantha">rakṣai <g type="pc"/></hi>
